The 4chan image downloader is a program that allows you to -no shit- download
all the images from a 4chan tread. By defining your own helpers you can also
make it download images from any 4chan-like message board.

Extending the program for other boards
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To bring extra functionality to the application and allow it to download
images from other 4chan-like boards, you have to create a helper.

A helper is a simple python script and should contain 2 functions. Here is the
template for a helper:

import re
import urllib

def make_url(board, tread):

def find_image_urls(url):
